:::The Destrocons:::

::They would have screamed if they had the movement capacity to do so, but 
since they didn't all three of their brains were drowned in a state of fear 
and confusion.  But soon anger started setting in.  All of them were thinking 
that if they ever got out of this, the Trainers would die slow and painful 
deaths::
